圖片顯示宿舍大堂的牆身，貼有小童繪畫支持警察的畫作，事主形容「很有愛呀」。事主在帖文亦圖文並茂，介紹自己獲安排「坐警車」，並附上事主自己與男友在警車內的自拍合照，又展示兩張從警車內，向外拍攝街道情況的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人指會了解事件，強調非常重視人員的操守，不容許警務人員作出違法或違紀的行為。如有個別警務人員涉嫌違法或違紀，警方會按既定機制公平公正調查及積極跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/27743445015/posts/10158314894520016/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F27743445015%2Fposts%2F10158314894520016%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=c35df9cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/27743445015/posts/10158314894520016/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"就係呢d臭雞屌動物<br />\n搞到有武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"8b198c74f497688d7c66576724693f8ef4ec66e7","tid":1849660,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf26b6193647b2eaf08b5561e7d4a74ff761046","tid":1849660,"uid":143220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"自推又點<br />\n反正都唔會有後果"},{"pid":"98b95c81b4e820bc0c66e7b521cfa5ead88f80b4","tid":1849660,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"狗仔狗女有特權"},{"pid":"e14fea477bcf090e4580d332baea6b6fa0f59650","tid":1849660,"uid":286558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6499e977c530e382d0bd803233f0e62b84a4aa52","tid":1849660,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"呢班畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b43bfad383b10a7575e6d47b1a249a48229a29","tid":1849660,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"Kwan Leung<br />\n<br />\n香港警察疑公器私用 安排警車接親友拜年 長髮女車內打卡上載微信被揭發<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/arsz